    <item>
      <title>布林肯希望以色列成为加沙袭击的更多目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-20/blinken-wants-israel-to-be-more-targeted-in-gaza-attacks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，以色列与哈马斯的战争需要进入“低强度阶段”。布林肯预计以色列将在加沙开展更有针对性的行动。他在华盛顿发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-20/blinken-wants-israel-to-be-more-targeted-in-gaza-attacks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 20:06:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于铜价暴跌导致债务膨胀，Codelco 被标准普尔双重下调评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/codelco-gets-double-downgrade-at-s-p-as-copper-slump-swells-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级将 Codelco 的信用评级下调了两级，原因是产量下滑促使这家全球最大的铜生产商提高了项目融资的债务水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/codelco-gets-double-downgrade-at-s-p-as-copper-slump-swells-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 19:50:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑对胡塞武装分子进行军事打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-20/us-considers-military-strikes-on-houthi-militants-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于胡塞武装在红海发动袭击，船舶保险费率飙升。与此同时，美国正在考虑对叛乱分子进行军事打击。彭博社的西蒙·凯西和凯莉·莱因茨报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-20/us-considers-military-strikes-on-houthi-militants-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 19:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行家预计 1 万亿美元蓝筹贷款市场在 2023 年放缓后将出现好转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/bankers-see-1-trillion-blue-chip-loan-market-turnaround-after-slow-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银行家预计美国蓝筹贷款市场的发行量将在 2024 年回升，此前今年利率上升在很大程度上使借款人保持观望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/bankers-see-1-trillion-blue-chip-loan-market-turnaround-after-slow-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 19:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
